These are the results of a survey on what young people do with their free time. {______________________________________ {AGE GROUP - 5-8 years
These children played mainly in parks and gardens near their homes. Games and activities include - BMX bikes, football and hide and seek. Pocket money on averge 55p per week. {______________________________________ {AGE GROUP - 8-17 years}
Most popular activities were - Scouts, Girl Guides and youth club. Hobbies include swimming, cycling, horse riding, squash and hiking. Some people thought there was not enough for young people to do. {______________________________________
